Module camp_management_and_application_system
Package interfaces

Interface ISuggestionCommitteeService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SuggestionCommitteeService
    public interface ISuggestionCommitteeService
    The ISuggestionCommitteeService interface defines a contract for classes that provide methods to manage suggestions submitted by students related to camps.
